{"data":[{"name":"94:1","price":"(1) Did We not expand for you, [O Muḥammad], your breast?[1944]","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَشۡرَحۡ لَكَ صَدۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6091,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1944]- i.e., enlighten, assure and gladden your heart with guidance.","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:2","price":"(2) And We removed from you your burden[1945]","arabic":"وَوَضَعۡنَا عَنكَ وِزۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6092,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1945]- By forgiving any errors which you may have committed previously or might commit consequently. \"Burden\" can also refer to the anxiety experienced by the Prophet (ﷺ) at the beginning of his mission.","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:3","price":"(3) Which had weighed upon your back","arabic":"ٱلَّذِيٓ أَنقَضَ ظَهۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6093,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:4","price":"(4) And raised high for you your repute.","arabic":"وَرَفَعۡنَا لَكَ ذِكۡرَكَ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6094,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:5","price":"(5) For indeed, with hardship [will be] ease [i.e., relief].","arabic":"فَإِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرًا","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6095,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:6","price":"(6) Indeed, with hardship [will be] ease.","arabic":"إِنَّ مَعَ ٱلۡعُسۡرِ يُسۡرٗا","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6096,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:7","price":"(7) So when you have finished [your duties], then stand up [for worship].","arabic":"فَإِذَا فَرَغۡتَ فَٱنصَبۡ","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6097,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"},{"name":"94:8","price":"(8) And to your Lord direct [your] longing.","arabic":"وَإِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَٱرۡغَب","category":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh"],"ayahNumber":6098,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"en"}],"chapter":["94 (Ash-Sharh)","Ash-Sharh","Surah Ash-Sharh","Chapter Ash-Sharh","Sharh","Surah Sharh","Chapter Sharh","Ash Sharh","Surah Ash Sharh","Chapter Ash Sharh","Surah 94","Chapter 94","The Relief","الشرح"]}